				I am a lvl 7 enchanter and can solo them if i play it right.All i do is cast lull on 2 of them them attack the other with Suffocating Sphere. Then i let my pet finish it off. The loot is really good for levels 5-7. The only problem is it usually gets camped often so if you see it empty, camp it for a while.
