				The bandits are a hard bunch to fight alone if they all attack at once.<BR>
Best to take a couple of Lvl 6-8's at least if nobody can Lull otherwise it gets a bit out of hand.<BR>
Sometimes they drop gems and jewellry, not worth much to merchants but great for a starting jeweller...I've had copper bands and (I think) they drop &quot;turquoise&quot;, if that's any use to a jeweller I don't know.<BR>
Keep an eye out particularly for the ones with spears (ouch!), they seem to be the ones that /con harder.
