	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is one of the first places nice people can start helping out the people weaker then them in Norrath. A level 10, maybe 9, can usually take a full spawn of all three bandits. Spawn patrol, as I call it ^_^. Con them first, you may want to be careful if they're all blue. Greens will come after you though, but blues are a sign of being extra tough. Also, some people have a little touble around here, so healers, nukers, and tanks can all serve a little helping hand here. The only thing to watch out for though is that I've found if you kill all three at once, they'll spawn almost all at the same time, making your help rather pointless, so try to spread the fights a little.
				</font>
